fb.rt.math
Interface FBStatus

public interface FBStatus

This interface provides the STATUS codes defined in Table D.1 of IEC 61499, plus an additional ARRAY_SIZE_ERROR code for MATRIX operations.

Field Summary
static int ACTION_CONTROL_CONTENTION
          Action control contention error in an SFC
static int ARRAY_SIZE_ERROR
          A MATRIX operation was attempted with invalid or inconsistent row or column counts
static int DIVISION_BY_0
          Division by zero or inversion of a singular matrix
